ng ph bo him y tr khi c tha thun khc.
i vi hp ng bo him u tin v hp ng bo him khng lin tc, hiu lc bo him tun theo
cc quy nh sau, tr khi c tha thun khc:
1

c hiu lc ngay sau khi Ngi c bo
him ng ph bo him y .;
2

365 ngy k t ngy hp ng c hiu lc.
3

30 ngy k t ngy hp ng c hiu lc.
4
m au bnh tt bt ng (khng phi do tai
nn):
Bo him ch c hiu lc sau 30 ngy k t
ngy hp ng c hiu lc.

365 ngy k t ngy hp ng c hiu lc.
6

bc s, ly u nang bung trng, iu tr thai sn:
90 ngy k t ngy hp ng c hiu lc.
7
Trng hp sinh :
270 ngy k t ngy hp ng c hiu lc.

LU KHI THU THP CHNG T BI THNG
Trng hp u quyn nhn tin bi thng h: phi c Giy y quyn nhn tin bi thng hp php.
Ho n thuc phi ph hp vi ch nh ca bc s iu tr v chng loi v s lng. Khng s dng 1 toa
thuc nhiu ln cho cc ho n thuc km theo.
n thuc phi ng quy nh ca B Y T v ch c gi tr trong 5 ngy, k t ngy ra n.
Ha n c s tin ln hn 200.000VN phi l ha n ti chnh (GTGT). Vic tch s tin trn
200.000VN thnh cc ho n bn l khng c chp nhn.
Cc ch nh xt nghim ca bc s m khng tm ra bnh hoc khng lin quan n vic iu tr bnh
tt th khng c bo him.
Cng ty Bo him c quyn yu cu bn chnh i chiu khi cn.
Ty trng hp, Cng ty Bo him c th yu cu cc chng t khc xc minh thng tin v lm c
s xem xt bi thng.
CC IM LOI TR CHNH
1. Hnh ng c ca Ngi c bo him hoc ngi tha k hp php (tr trng hp ngi tha
k l tr em di 14 tui).
2. Ngi c bo him b nh hng trc tip do s dng ru, bia, ma ty hoc cc cht kch thch
tng t khc.
3. Ngi c bo him vi phm nghim trng php lut, ni quy, quy nh ca chnh quyn a
phng hoc cc t chc x hi.
4. iu tr hoc s dng thuc khng theo hng dn ca c s y t.
5. iu dng, an dng.
6. Nm vin kim tra sc khe hoc khm gim nh y khoa m khng lin quan n vic iu tr
bnh tt.
7. iu tr hoc phu thut cc bnh tt bm sinh, nhng thng tt v ch nh phu thut c t trc
ngy bt u bo him.
8. iu tr cha c khoa hc cng nhn hoc iu tr th nghim.
9. To hnh thm m, chnh hnh, phc hi chc nng, lm chn, tay gi, mt gi, rng gi.
10. K hoch ha gia nh.
11. Bnh c bit, bnh c sn: im loi tr ny ch p dng trong nm u tin k t ngy bt u bo
him.
12. Ngi c bo him mc cc bnh giang mai, lu, nhim vi rt HIV, st rt, lao v bnh ngh
nghip.
13. Hot ng hng khng (tr khi vi t cch l hnh khch c v), cc cuc din tp, hun luyn qun
s, tham gia chin u ca cc lc lng v trang.
14. Ngi c bo him tham gia nh nhau tr khi c xc nhn l hnh ng t v.
15. ng t, ni la, nhim phng x.
16. Chin tranh, ni chin, nh cng.
17. Khng b.
THI HN THNG BO S KIN BO HIM
V THI HN YU CU TR TIN BO HIM
Cng ty bo him c trch nhim xem xt, gii quyt v thanh ton tin bo him trong vng 15 ngy
k t khi nhn c y h s hp l, tr khi c tha thun khc.
Thi hn Ngi c bo him hoc ngi tha k hp php khiu ni Cng ty bo him v quyt
nh tr tin bo him l 06 thng k t ngy Ngi c bo him hoc ngi tha k hp php nhn
c thng bo tr tin bo him. Thi hiu khi kin v hp ng bo him l 03 nm k t ngy pht
sinh tranh chp.
CCH THC TI APP
QUN L N BO HIM V NP H S, THEO DI H S BI THNG
Ngoi cch gi giy chng nhn bo him v np h s bi thng truyn thng, qu khch vui lng ti
App "SAS Health Concierge", c th theo di n bo him (quyn li bo him chi tit) v np h s
bi thng cng nh theo di qu trnh x l h s trc tuyn theo thi gian thc.
Cch thc ti app:
CCH 1: ti ng dng theo m QR
Icon APP "SAS Health Concierge"
Dnh cho App Store
Dnh cho Google Play
CCH 2:
Bc 1: Tm t kha "SAS Health Concierge" trn Appstore hoc CH Play
Bc 2: Chn "Ci t" hoc "Ti xung"
Np h s trc tuyn:
Bc 1: Chn "Gi yu cu Bi thng"
Bc 2: in thng tin c nhn theo yu cu (bao gm: Ngi yu cu bi thng, C s y t, S ha n,
Ngy iu tr / Ngy nhp vin, Quyn li bo him, S tin yu cu bi thng)
Bc 3: Nhp Email & S in thoi
Bc 4: Nhp thng tin "Chn on" v "Lu thm ca Bc s" (nu c)
Bc 5: Ti chng t ln (bao gm: Giy ngh bi thng, Chng t y t, Chng t ti chnh)
Bc 6: Chn "Ti ln" hoc "Chp hnh"
Bc 7: Chn "Np h s"
Tra cu h s Bi thng:
Bc 1: T mn hnh chnh, chn "H s bi thng"
Bc 2: Xem trng thi x l v chi tit h s, Tm Bnh vin/Phng khm
Bc 3: Xem ti mc "Lch s tm kim"
Bc 4: Theo di tin trnh h s
* Ti liu ny ch l bng tm tt, chi tit xin vui lng tham kho bng hng dn s dng App v
cch thc np h s bi thng
